ot be added to the snapshotter at this time."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any multipoint, multipolyline, multipolygon, shape or point collection"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that is specified is silently ignored."}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotation:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotation:"},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"addAnnotation:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapSnapshotter(im)addAnnotation:"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","title":"MLNPolyline","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPolyline"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"specified as "},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the line segments that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path along which something moves."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapSnapshotter","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" generates static raster images of the map. Each snapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image depicts a portion of a map defined by an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you provide. The snapshotter generates an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"asynchronously, calling "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" methods if defined, then"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"passing it into a completion handler once tiles and other resources needed for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the snapshot are finished loading."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotter"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshot":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshot","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapSnapshot","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An image generated by a snapshotter object."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshot"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotOptions":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotoptions","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The options to use when creating images with the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNPointCollection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"disconnected vertices, specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances. The"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"orchard.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPointCollection"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter/addAnnotation:":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the snapshotter."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotati